| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2528 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a3d05b08-14a4-50b6-b7c1-99335d97aadd"
